  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Now</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/950ac8a7ca128a50794e0117aea1b7b9.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=188 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take the Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deivy</strong> made a pact with Randoom, he would be his toy and go through all of Randoom's challenges in exchange for having anything he wanted after it was over. Now Deivy has been turned into a chess piece and is trapped in <strong>Randoom's mansion</strong>, a dangerous place full of <strong>challenges</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Trials of Randoom?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trials of Randoom</strong> is a precision platformer with puzzle elements, featuring Deivy and his terrifying situation in search of freedom and <strong>salvation</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Who is Deivy?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deivy was once an ordinary human. Too common. He became a pawn to participate in Random's challenges, as he was so desperate that he would do absolutely anything to achieve his goal, even making a pact with a demon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Mighty Random</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random is what some call the crossroads demon, but this crossroads story is just a popular myth, as he can show himself anywhere. It appears when someone is in a completely hopeless situation. When a person is so hopeless and ready to accept anything, that's when he offers his deals. He makes fun of people in exchange for helping them with their problems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/8d57aa53d8dc0056e05b96df00313a80.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Mansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mansion, in which Deivy is imprisoned, is special. Deivy's movements are limited by the powers of the mansion, making every challenge even more difficult!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The challenges in the mansion are very diverse. Will Deivy make it through them all?!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/950ac8a7ca128a50794e0117aea1b7b9.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=188 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take the Challenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deivy</strong> made a pact with Randoom, he would be his toy and go through all of Randoom's challenges in exchange for having anything he wanted after it was over. Now Deivy has been turned into a chess piece and is trapped in <strong>Randoom's mansion</strong>, a dangerous place full of <strong>challenges</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/dadf8b0a68ba9479982d75b5f50cc5c8.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What is Trials of Randoom?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trials of Randoom</strong> is a precision platformer with puzzle elements, featuring Deivy and his terrifying situation in search of freedom and <strong>salvation</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/e6d0da02b3da8eb561ace9b0eaad7825.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Who is Deivy?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deivy was once an ordinary human. Too common. He became a pawn to participate in Random's challenges, as he was so desperate that he would do absolutely anything to achieve his goal, even making a pact with a demon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.poster.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.webm?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/2c8b8c7d373cf87574650aaae7162a03.mp4?t=1738582575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Mighty Random</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random is what some call the crossroads demon, but this crossroads story is just a popular myth, as he can show himself anywhere. It appears when someone is in a completely hopeless situation. When a person is so hopeless and ready to accept anything, that's when he offers his deals. He makes fun of people in exchange for helping them with their problems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435410/extras/8d57aa53d8dc0056e05b96df00313a80.avif?t=1738582575\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Mansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mansion, in which Deivy is imprisoned, is special. Deivy's movements are limited by the powers of the mansion, making every challenge even more difficult!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The challenges in the mansion are very diverse. Will Deivy make it through them all?!</p></li></ul>",
